WEBVTT

00:04:29.999 --> 00:04:31.252
human beings.

00:04:33.089 --> 00:04:36.903
This, we are finally realizing,
is where healing happens.

00:04:37.673 --> 00:04:41.193
Yes, compassion -- literally,
as we learned yesterday --

00:04:41.217 --> 00:04:42.645
suffering together.

00:04:44.672 --> 00:04:48.010
Now, on the systems side,
on the other hand,

00:04:48.034 --> 00:04:51.892
so much of the suffering
is unnecessary, invented.

00:04:52.376 --> 00:04:54.650
It serves no good purpose.

00:04:54.674 --> 00:04:58.975
But the good news is,
since this brand of suffering is made up,

00:04:58.999 --> 00:05:00.483
well, we can change it.